data.title: Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan's Voice Offers A Sonic Refuge
data.meta_description: Right before he recorded a string of beloved albums for Peter Gabriel's label, the Pakistani vocal master of qawwali gave a milestone performance in 1985. It's now available for the first time.
